title: ETP-12_SingleCell_A10_S361
characteristics_ch1: who classification: ETP-ALL__tissue (isolated from): NSG spleen
extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells

extract_protocol_ch1: PBMCs were isolated using Ficoll-Paque, stained with anti-CD45 FITC. Live single cells were sorted into 96 well plates containing TCL buffer.__Full-length single cell RNA-seq libraries were prepared using the SMART-seq2 protocol. cDNA was fragmented using Nextera XT (Illumina) and amplified with indexed Nextera PCR primers.
data_processing: Adapter trimming was performed using trimmomatic version 0.36__Sequence quality was assessed using fastqc version 0.11.5__Alignment agains human genome was performed using START version 2.5.2b using following parameters -  --twopassMode Basic          --alignIntronMax 100000 --alignMatesGapMax 100000   --alignSJDBoverhangMin 10   --alignSJstitchMismatchNmax 5   -1   5   5 --outSAMstrandField intronMotif --outSAMattributes NH HI NM MD AS XS__Raw counts were obtained from aligned bam files using htseq version 0.9.1__Genome_build: hg19__Supplementary_files_format_and_content: htseq count file with raw counts for all the human genes for individual cells
